	<h2>Glass Events</h2>
	<h3>Group event planner focusing on transparency.</h2>
	<p>First project during the Web Development Immersive at General Assembly.  Focus for the project was Ruby on Rails and data modeling.</p>
	
	<h4>Features</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Allows users to track the progress of the planning of an event.</li>
		<li>Users can see which event organizers are fullfiling certain tasks.</li>
		<li>Users can see quotes for services being considered.</li>
		<li>Users can track event costs as providers are chosen for each service.</li>
	</ul>

	<h4>Technical Features</h4>
	<ul>
		<li>Custom user authorizations, featuring multiple user levels.</li>
		<li>Strong data model, tracking all user interacation with the event planning process.</li>
		<li>Ruby on Rails, HTML, CSS, Foundation Framework.</li>
	</ul>
	
